WEBVTT

00:00:00.439 --> 00:00:08.219
Good morning, family. Thank you for joining us again today. We have some things to pray about. You see it all in the news.

00:00:08.220 --> 00:00:21.127
The Lord warned me today and He said, 'Brandon, what you're seeing right now in the news, all that's going on—I told you all BlackRock was a bad and evil company.

00:00:21.128 --> 00:00:45.748
I told you that there would be key people in the financial sector that will try to come against President Trump's agenda and what he's trying to do to make America great again.'And we're seeing that as he tries to take steps forward, we're seeing them come against him with the stock market, with crypto, and with all these other things.

00:00:45.749 --> 00:00:54.015
When he says, 'We're going to go this way,'they try to sink the stock market; they try to sink the financial stability of the dollar.

00:00:54.016 --> 00:00:59.035
We're seeing what the Lord showed me come to pass right in front of our faces.

00:00:59.036 --> 00:01:20.886
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, you must stand in the gap and pray as watchmen on the wall for President Trump, for the administration, for Elon Musk, and for the agenda of what he's trying to do,'because what he is doing is aligning with what the Lord is wanting to bring forth.

00:01:20.887 --> 00:01:32.236
The wealth transfer is going to come out of this, and this is what's going to bring forth the end-time harvest.

00:01:32.237 --> 00:01:41.528
It all goes like dominoes. As we see them resist and come against him, it's the demonic entities.

00:01:41.529 --> 00:01:48.959
We wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities, powers, and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:02:00.513
We're wrestling against the demonic trying to stop the end-time wealth transfer and stop what God is going to do.

00:02:00.514 --> 00:02:21.576
He's going to do it, but we're experiencing resistance because they've had their hand in the cookie jar for years through the Bush Administration, the Clinton Administration, and the Obama Administration—decade after decade.

00:02:21.577 --> 00:02:27.490
We've seen a good forty years of them having their hand in the cookie jar.

00:02:27.491 --> 00:02:34.251
It wasn't so much with the Reagan administration, but with the Carter one for sure.

00:02:34.252 --> 00:02:42.754
It's amazing to see what the Lord has been talking to me about over the last twenty-four hours, saying, 'Brandon, this is what you're called to do.

00:02:42.755 --> 00:02:56.759
We're going to pray over this administration so that they are able to do what God has called them to do, bringing forth the wealth transfer.'The sky's not falling.

00:02:56.760 --> 00:03:00.111
The stock market and crypto are tanking because they are trying to stir things up.

00:03:00.112 --> 00:03:14.422
It's like an animal flapping its wings because it's upset; they don't want anyone touching what they have.

00:03:14.423 --> 00:03:24.869
It's basically about the child pedophile and child trafficking rings.

00:03:24.870 --> 00:03:39.972
President Trump is coming against this demonic stronghold of the banking cartel that has been in place with the Democratic Party.

00:03:39.973 --> 00:03:45.739
He's saying we're not going to do this anymore and we're going down a different path.

00:03:45.740 --> 00:04:10.272
As they try to come against that, they say, 'Let's cause the stock market to crash.'When he deals with Justin Trudeau—whether he's been replaced or not, I've seen him being replaced with a new Prime Minister over Canada.

00:04:10.273 --> 00:04:33.441
We see this new shift and a new direction. The Lord showed me today, 'Brandon, this is what you're interceding for: the wealth transfer and this major harvest of souls about to take place.'God is about to show up and show off in your life.

00:04:33.442 --> 00:04:39.128
I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, it's time for you to believe Him for big things.

00:04:39.129 --> 00:04:49.119
He said there is a display of the glory of the Lord that will be on our faces like we've never seen before.

00:04:49.120 --> 00:05:04.235
When we enter an atmosphere, the manifested presence of God will be there.

00:05:04.236 --> 00:05:18.406
We've seen the anointing before, but I'm talking about a tangible presence of the Lord on people in grocery stores, gas stations, and churches.

00:05:18.407 --> 00:05:28.300
There will be a manifested presence on us even before the glory shows up.

00:05:28.301 --> 00:05:45.877
It will be that level of being God-inside minded and filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:05:45.878 --> 00:06:10.860
It will shine on our faces like it did for Moses. Those who are all in will carry a presence of the Lord like never before. He said, 'Brandon, I'm going to set the captives free.

00:06:10.861 --> 00:06:29.082
I'm coming back for a church without spot or wrinkle.'When this greater glory comes, you will see a burden-removing, yoke-destroying power.

00:06:29.083 --> 00:06:38.411
You're going to see the demonic manifest because they haven't been challenged for a long time.

00:06:38.412 --> 00:07:06.122
We're going to see it challenged with the glory of the Lord because it's truly God manifesting on us, shining on our faces.

00:07:06.123 --> 00:07:30.308
When fire comes, it makes the evil manifest. We're not walking in fear, but in authority.

00:07:30.309 --> 00:07:46.896
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, you're going to see more devils manifest than ever before because so many people are walking around with demonic oppression.'We're not going to tolerate it; we're going to take our dominion and cast these devils out.

00:07:46.897 --> 00:08:17.326
The 'spot'is demonic oppression—people oppressed by depression, anxiety, fear, sexual perversion, alcohol, and lust.

00:08:17.327 --> 00:08:25.263
The Lord said, 'I've come to set the captives free.'He whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:08:25.264 --> 00:08:32.140
People will walk in the divine manifestations of the glory.

00:08:32.141 --> 00:08:49.666
He said, 'Brandon, I'm going to provoke the world through you with financial blessing.'Satan doesn't want to see the body of Christ blessed.

00:08:49.667 --> 00:09:05.624
As they persecute you for the blessing, He said, 'I'm going to increase it even greater because they're persecuting the God inside of you.'The thermostat is turning up.

00:09:05.625 --> 00:09:05.724
Great favor is coming—an acceleration of favor that would normally take days of hard labor.

00:09:05.725 --> 00:10:18.999
It's a God-possession; He is dwelling in you. He said, 'I have streets paved with gold.

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:36.842
Rubies and diamonds are just my handiwork, and I've given them to the sons of men to enjoy.'This wealth transfer and endowment of glory is here now.

00:10:36.843 --> 00:10:49.131
Start tapping into it by practicing the presence of the Lord.

00:10:49.132 --> 00:11:08.474
I saw a glorious church rising without spot or wrinkle, and days of great shaking are coming—a shaking to awakening.

00:11:08.475 --> 00:11:39.579
When they can't stop it, they try to sink the economy or start rumors of war.

00:11:39.580 --> 00:11:41.415
The next thing coming is a plague. They will try to sink everything with a new plague worse than COVID.

00:11:41.416 --> 00:12:06.837
I saw billions of people affected by this world pandemic. The Lord sounded the alarm to the watchmen.

00:12:06.838 --> 00:12:23.760
There's a financial crisis trying to sink the dollar. I saw President Trump interceding in the White House, shocking the land back to life.

00:12:23.761 --> 00:12:31.701
As people humble themselves and pray, He will heal our land.

00:12:31.702 --> 00:13:02.488
I saw a glorious church with a 'honey glow'—the anointing of the Holy Spirit—laying hands on the sick and seeing them recover.

00:13:02.489 --> 00:13:17.479
A mighty moving army, like in Tommy Hicks'vision, is rising to take the glory to the nations.

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:30.078
We're praying for the end of abortion and for the righteous to take authority over demonic spirits.

00:13:30.079 --> 00:14:01.559
We are seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above principalities and powers.

00:14:01.560 --> 00:14:53.062
You must prophesy and decree a thing from a higher level. Whatever you bind on earth is bound in heaven.

00:14:53.063 --> 00:15:09.339
Put on your armor. It wasn't designed for retreat, but for taking dominion. Joshua and Caleb weren't afraid of giants.

00:15:09.340 --> 00:15:38.919
Who are the Davids who will take the land and not be intimidated by this uncircumcised Philistine? We have dominion because we're God-inside minded.

00:15:38.920 --> 00:15:47.714
It's going to take the new Reinhard Bonnkes, the new George Whitefields, the new William Seymours, and the John G.

00:15:47.715 --> 00:16:41.677
Lakes to say, 'Satan, we're taking the land back for Jesus.'We've never seen the wells of revival that are about to come on the I-35 corridor—uninterrupted glory.

00:16:41.678 --> 00:16:47.675
The Devil himself has visited my house twice, and he is a defeated foe.

00:16:47.676 --> 00:17:17.826
He could not stand against the blood or the glory. We have the greater one inside of us.

00:17:17.827 --> 00:17:59.967
It's time to get radical and not be cowards. All you need is one glorious moment with the Lord to be forever changed.

00:17:59.968 --> 00:18:47.053
Just a touch of the hem of His garment, like the woman with the issue of blood who was made whole.

00:18:47.054 --> 00:19:01.292
Father, we thank You in the name of Jesus. We take authority over our finances.

00:19:01.293 --> 00:19:15.079
Angelic host, go out now and cause the money to come forth. Satan, release our money!

00:19:15.080 --> 00:19:31.473
Cease and desist your maneuvering against our finances. We call for blessing, increase, and favor.

00:19:31.474 --> 00:19:39.664
We take authority over poverty and lack. The spirit of infirmity is broken off our lives.

00:19:39.665 --> 00:20:32.076
The glory of the Lord rests on our countenance. When we walk into a place of business, we have great favor.

00:20:32.077 --> 00:20:49.702
Father, we take authority over the crypto market. You showed me demonic spirits are influencing it.

00:20:49.703 --> 00:21:07.446
We take back the land. We pray for President Trump and a hedge of protection around him. No weapon formed against him shall prosper.

00:21:07.447 --> 00:21:27.341
