Plagues are coming, but we're not like Chicken Little; the sky is not falling.

00:28:15.616 --> 00:28:36.249
We are radically filled with God. Rejoice and be glad. I enjoy this park and God's handiwork.

00:28:36.250 --> 00:29:18.920
Thank You for healing and deliverance. We're free by the blood.

00:29:18.921 --> 00:29:57.680
Thank You for a divine turnaround in this nation. We will not shrink back; we will walk in abundance.

00:29:57.681 --> 00:31:07.076
